.repo-audit-findings.md
*.scratch.md

# Local testing / dogfooding — if harness-steward is ever used on itself,
# sediment at the repo root should NOT be committed to the shipped bundle.
# But the worked example's .harness/ IS part of the distribution (it's
# the whole point of the example), so scope the ignore to repo root only.
/.harness/
